high_descs: Walk to the counter in front of you then turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the fridge and turn left to face it.
Put the knife in the green up that's in the fridge.
Pick up the green cup with the knife in it and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the stool then turn right and walk to the sink.,
Put the green cup in the center of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk over to the fridge, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the butter knife in the green cup that is inside the fridge.
Take the green cup with the butter knife in it out of the fridge ad close the fridge door.
Turn around and walk towards the oven, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Put the green cup with the butter knife in it into the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a green cup with a knife in it in the left sink basin.

high_descs: Turn to the left to find the sink.
Pick up the knife, just in front of the sink.
Take the knife and turn around, then face the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge and place the knife inside the green glass.
Take out the green glass and knife from the fridge, and shut the door.
Take the glass and turn left to find the sink.
Place the glass and knife inside the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife and glass to the sink.
